      <abstract encodinganalog="5203_">James C. Garlington was a Missoula,
		  Montana, attorney elected as a delegate to the 1972 Montana Constitutional
		  Convention. The collection consists of Garlington's papers from the 1972
		  Montana Constitutional Convention.</abstract>
